    <div class="flexibleblocks">
    <section class="flexibleblocks-block __nomargin">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row offset-xl-1">
                <div class="col-12 col-xl-11">
                    <div class="imagetext __animate __alt">
                            <div class="imagetext-image">
                                <img src="/media/3lyn2dll/busnes01lliw.jpg?anchor=center&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=650&amp;height=430&amp;rnd=132706494921030000" alt="Photo of person completing application form on laptop" data-object-fit="cover">
                            </div>
                        <div class="imagetext-body">
                            <div class="usercontent">
                                <p><strong>How to apply?</strong></p>
<p>Fluency in both written and spoken Welsh is essential for all our roles as we operate predominately in the Welsh language. In turn, all job applications should be submitted in Welsh using the form below.</p>
<p>Completed <a href="/media/zhjommi0/ffurflen-gais-electronigword.doc" title="Ffurflen Gais Electronigword (3)">application forms</a> should be sent to <a href="mailto:swyddi@cyg-wlc.cymru">swyddi@cyg-wlc.cymru </a>by the date noted on the job description. If possible please also complete the <a href="/media/05zbamo2/ffurflen-monitro-cydraddoldeb.docx" title="Ffurflen Monitro Cydraddoldeb">equality monitoring form</a></p>
<p>If you have a question or query about working for the Welsh Language Commissioner, please <a href="/contact-us" title="(Contact Us)">contact us</a>.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

